#. +> stable5
#: powerdevil.notifyrc:484
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid "Your battery has reached low level"
msgstr "バッテリ残量が低レベルに達しました"

#. +> trunk6 stable6 stable5
#: powerdevil.notifyrc:557
msgctxt "Name"
msgid "Battery Critical"
msgstr "バッテリ危険レベル"

#. +> trunk6 stable6
#: powerdevil.notifyrc:613
#, fuzzy
#| msgctxt "Comment"
#| msgid ""
#| "Your battery has reached critical level. This notification triggers a "
#| "countdown before doing the configured action, hence it is strongly "
#| "advised to leave that on."
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid ""
"Battery has reached critical level. This notification triggers a countdown "
"before doing the configured action, hence it is strongly advised to leave it "
"on."
msgstr ""
"バッテリ残量が危険レベルに達しました。この通知によって、このレベルに設定され"
"ているアクションのカウントダウンが開始されるので、有効にしておくことを強くお"
"勧めします。"

#. +> stable5
#: powerdevil.notifyrc:596
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid ""
"Your battery has reached critical level. This notification triggers a "
"countdown before doing the configured action, hence it is strongly advised "
"to leave that on."
msgstr ""
"バッテリ残量が危険レベルに達しました。この通知によって、このレベルに設定され"
"ているアクションのカウントダウンが開始されるので、有効にしておくことを強くお"
"勧めします。"

